     C* G25: O-spec ADD. Cycle reads ADATA (10,20,30), appends each VAL
     C* to output DISK file AOUT via ADD. AOUT holds 10/20/30.
     FADATA   IP  F      80            DISK
     FAOUT    O   F      80            DISK
     IADATA      01
     I                                        1   20VAL
     OAOUT    DADD
     O                         VAL        2
